data.description: You will love this almost new Piedmont Residential home with 4 Bedrooms and 2.5 Baths! Rocking chair front porch invites you in! 2-Story foyer! LVP floors throughout the Main! Living Room and Dining Room adjoin for a large entertaining space! Great Room with Gas Fireplace! Spacious Kitchen with Island, Granite Counters, Stainless Steel Appliances & Pantry! Large Master Retreat with Tray Ceiling! Master Bath with Dual Vanities, Glass Shower, Soaking tub & Large Walk-in Closet! 3 additional Bedrooms, Full Bathroom & Laundry Room upstairs! Poured back patio perfect for evening dinners! Fenced Backyard, complete with Grill & Garden area! Shed for all your lawn equipment, remains! Fun in the sun with the Community Pool & Playground! Run to this one!
